The paper also mentions speech recognition and machine translation, which are applications of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of sequential statistics, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CL, followed by cs.AI, cs.CR, and cs.IT.
